result.notes: A comprehensive record of recreational dives off Dorset since the mid 1970s. A paper log of each dive records the location; conditions; photos taken and sightings/items of interest. In addition, the paper records are supported by an extensive collection of slides which are labelled with species name, site and date all held by the recorder.
